Here's a PlantUML component diagram focusing on the connectivity aspect of the system:

```plantuml
@startuml davidlandry93_glo4001

skinparam componentStyle uml2

[3D Rendering Core] as rendering
[Robotic Control] as robotics
[Data Handling] as data
[CZML Processing] as czml
[Point Cloud Processing] as pointcloud
[Sensor Data Acquisition] as sensors
[ROS Integration] as ros

interface "WebGL API" as webgl
interface "ROS Topics" as rostopics
interface "File I/O" as fileio

rendering -( webgl
rendering ..> data : uses
rendering ..> pointcloud : renders

robotics ..> ros : communicates via
robotics ..> sensors : manages
robotics ..> data : processes

data ..> fileio : reads/writes
data ..> czml : parses

ros -( rostopics

sensors ..> ros : subscribes to
sensors ..> pointcloud : generates

pointcloud ..> data : transforms

czml ..> data : provides

@enduml
```